Exos Combine Class of 2024

NFL Exos

When it comes to Exos and the NFL combine, the numbers speak for themself. Exos have been preparing American Football athletes for the biggest interview of their lives for 20 years. Lets take a look into the stats for the 2024 season.

Jess De Silva
03-08-2024

107 American Football athletes joined Exos for their 2024 8-week NFL combine preparation program. Across these 8 weeks, athletes gain access to world class coaches and facilities for physical evaluation, performance training, physical therapy, and nutrition.
